items.badge_description: When it comes to a delicious beer from the Netherlands, going Dutch doesn’t have to mean sharing it. That's 5 different beers from a brewery from the Netherlands. Try 5 more Level 2.

Round and round the wheel goes! Which style you’ll be drinking, nobody knows! Your desire to explore different styles is inspiring. Keep it up! That's a check-in to at least 30 different styles. Try 5 more for Level 7!
When it comes to a delicious beer from the Netherlands, going Dutch doesn’t have to mean sharing it. That's 130 different beers from the Netherlands. Try 5 more Level 27
It's New Brew Thursday! Drink a new beer on three Thursdays in a 30 day period! Find out how New Brew Thursday was started, and catch up on old episodes.
After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren't you?. That's 105 different Lagers! Try 5 more to unlock Level 22.

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 45 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 10!
Travel much? You must be a "brewsetter". That's at least 5 beers from 5 different countries.
